00:38:58.676 --> 00:39:00.866 A:middle
making apps accessible, but we

00:39:00.916 --> 00:39:02.106 A:middle
can do better.

00:39:03.326 --> 00:39:05.676 A:middle
We can and we should provide our

00:39:05.676 --> 00:39:06.976 A:middle
users with exceptional,

00:39:07.196 --> 00:39:08.706 A:middle
delightful experiences that

00:39:08.706 --> 00:39:09.976 A:middle
cater to their unique needs.

00:39:11.726 --> 00:39:12.926 A:middle
There are a lot of ways to take

00:39:12.926 --> 00:39:14.096 A:middle
an accessible app from being

00:39:14.096 --> 00:39:15.496 A:middle
functional to being exceptional.

00:39:16.836 --> 00:39:18.146 A:middle
Designing for accessibility up

00:39:18.146 --> 00:39:20.066 A:middle
front can get you a lot of wins.

00:39:20.496 --> 00:39:21.946 A:middle
Doing things like making sure

00:39:21.946 --> 00:39:23.096 A:middle
your colors meet minimum

00:39:23.096 --> 00:39:25.446 A:middle
recommended contrast ratios or

00:39:25.446 --> 00:39:27.056 A:middle
that your layout can adequately

00:39:27.056 --> 00:39:29.226 A:middle
adapt to changing size have

00:39:29.226 --> 00:39:30.956 A:middle
benefits for all users.

00:39:31.616 --> 00:39:33.216 A:middle
But you should also extend you

00:39:33.216 --> 00:39:34.906 A:middle
default design to accommodate

00:39:34.906 --> 00:39:36.076 A:middle
the settings that users have

00:39:36.076 --> 00:39:36.496 A:middle
enabled.

00:39:38.066 --> 00:39:39.116 A:middle
Finally, when crafting the

00:39:39.116 --> 00:39:41.126 A:middle
accessibility experience for

00:39:41.126 --> 00:39:43.206 A:middle
assistive technologies, do so

00:39:43.206 --> 00:39:44.046 A:middle
purposefully.

00:39:44.856 --> 00:39:46.126 A:middle
Prioritize your content.

00:39:46.536 --> 00:39:47.966 A:middle
Make it easy and intuitive to

00:39:47.966 --> 00:39:50.046 A:middle
navigate and provide context

00:39:50.046 --> 00:39:50.786 A:middle
when necessary.

00:39:52.486 --> 00:39:54.336 A:middle
For more information as well as

00:39:54.336 --> 00:39:56.126 A:middle
access to a simplified finished

00:39:56.126 --> 00:39:57.646 A:middle
version of the sample app you

00:39:57.646 --> 00:39:59.386 A:middle
saw there, you can visit our

